Text: How current is this encyclopedia? Does it cover Dust's profile?

This pack contains both v1(2002) and v2 (2006) of The Marvel Encyclopedia, but not v3 which was published in October 2009.  Neither The Marvel Encyclopedia or the X-Men Encyclopedia contain profiles of Dust (Sooraya Qadir) as far as I am aware.
Thanks a lot for this, I'll seed for a while.
